# IAM profile three-layer boundary — IDE anti-drift contract

**Canonical decisions:** [ADR-0034](docs/decisions/0034-neon-auth-iam-profile-surface.md) (Neon runtime matrix) · [ADR-0035](docs/decisions/0035-three-layer-surface-ide-anti-drift.md) (AGENTS.md **PRIORITY #2**) · Layer 1 seal: [`app/(main)/[locale]/o/[orgSlug]/iam-profile/_SEAL.md`](../../app/(main)/[locale]/o/[orgSlug]/iam-profile/_SEAL.md)

**If this rule and `AGENTS.md` diverge, follow `AGENTS.md` and fix this rule in the same PR.**

Org-scoped member IAM uses **one product name everywhere: `iam-profile`**.  
URL segment is **`/o/{slug}/iam-profile/*`** — not `/profile/`. Legacy `/account` redirects session-aware to this tree.

Mechanical guard: [`tests/unit/iam-profile-surface-contract.test.ts`](tests/unit/iam-profile-surface-contract.test.ts)

---

## Prime directive (read before any edit)

```txt
Layer 1 — app/           → URL + thin re-exports ONLY (layout may own Tier A shell)
Layer 2 — lib/features/  → page orchestrators, data, actions, metadata
Layer 3 — components2/   → client islands + presentation ONLY
```

**Import doors (only these):**

| Layer | Door |
| --- | --- |
| Layer 2 | `#features/iam-profile` · `#features/iam-profile/server` |
| Layer 3 | `#components2/iam-profile/*` |
| Client actions | `#features/iam-profile/client` |

**IAM control plane** (session guards, audit) stays in `#lib/auth` — not this module.

---

## Layer 1 — `app/.../o/[orgSlug]/iam-profile/`

**Owns:** route files, `_SEAL.md`, layout Tier A (`OrgIamProfileDeferredShell`).

**Allowed in leaf `page.tsx`:**

```tsx
export { IamProfileOverviewPage as default } from "#features/iam-profile/server"

export {
  generateIamProfileIdentityMetadata as generateMetadata,
  IamProfileIdentityPage as default,
} from "#features/iam-profile/server"
```

**Forbidden in leaf `page.tsx`:**

| Action | Why |
| --- | --- |
| `getProfileShellData`, `listDeviceSessions`, session guards | Layer 2 |
| `AppShellSurface`, overview/identity/security JSX | Layer 2 orchestrators |
| `#components2/iam-profile` imports in routes | Layer 3 via Layer 2 only |
| `#features/nexus` in `"use client"` files | Use `#features/nexus/client` |

---

## Layer 2 — `lib/features/iam-profile/`

**Owns:** Neon-backed profile mutations, shell data, metadata, RSC page bodies.

**Allowed module root entries only** ([`scripts/check-agent-contract.mjs`](scripts/check-agent-contract.mjs)):

```txt
actions/ · data/ · components/ · schemas/ · index.ts · server.ts · client.ts · types.ts · constants.ts · *.contract.ts · README.md
```

**Forbidden at `lib/features/iam-profile/` root:**

| Entry | Why |
| --- | --- |
| `_SEAL.md` | Not allowed — use route `_SEAL.md` |
| `profile-metadata.server.ts` loose at root | Belongs in `data/` |
| `profile-shell.types.ts` loose at root | Belongs in `schemas/` |
| Passkey / 2FA / `changeEmail` flows | ADR-0034 — Neon unsupported |

**Canonical Layer 2 files:**

| Concern | Path |
| --- | --- |
| Public barrel | `index.ts` · `server.ts` · `client.ts` |
| Metadata | `data/profile-metadata.server.ts` |
| Shell / overview data | `data/profile-shell-data.server.ts` |
| Rail types | `schemas/profile-shell.types.shared.ts` |
| Page orchestrators | `components/iam-profile-*-page.server.tsx` |
| Deferred shell | `components/org-iam-profile-deferred-shell.tsx` |
| Mutations | `actions/*.actions.ts` |

---

## Layer 3 — `components2/iam-profile/`

**Owns:** compound client providers + panels for identity, security, overview sections.

| File | Role |
| --- | --- |
| `iam-profile-identity.client.tsx` | Provider + panels mount |
| `iam-profile-security.client.tsx` | Provider + panels mount |
| `iam-profile-overview-sections.client.tsx` | Overview next / membership / danger |
| `iam-profile-*-panels.client.tsx` | Panel bodies |
| `iam-profile-*-context.client.tsx` | Client state + action wiring |

**May import:** `#components2/ui/*`, `#features/iam-profile/client`, `#i18n/navigation`.

**Forbidden in Layer 3:**

| Action | Why |
| --- | --- |
| `#features/iam-profile` server barrel | ADR-0030 |
| `#lib/auth` server barrel | Client boundary |
| Passkey, 2FA, `changeEmail`, `/account/` fallbacks | ADR-0034 |

---

## Neon unsupported (do not add until documented)

Passkeys · 2FA · `changeEmail` · avatar `updateUser({ image })`

---

## Verification (required after every iam-profile task)

```bash
pnpm lint:path -- lib/features/iam-profile components2/iam-profile
pnpm test:fast -- tests/unit/iam-profile-surface-contract.test.ts
pnpm typecheck
```

`pnpm lint:agent-contract` must not report forbidden entries under `lib/features/iam-profile/`.

---

## Parity reference (same three-layer shape)

| Surface | Layer 1 `app/` | Layer 2 `lib/` | Layer 3 `components2/` |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Pre-login auth | `(auth)/` | `lib/auth/` (control plane) | `components2/auth/` |
| Legal-docs | `legal-docs/` | `lib/features/legal-docs/` | `components2/legal-docs/` |
| IAM profile | `o/.../iam-profile/` | `lib/features/iam-profile/` | `components2/iam-profile/` |

When unsure: **routes stay thin, features own truth, components own paint.**
